Ford DiagNow Privacy Policy
Effective: November 4, 2021
SUMMARY
This Privacy Policy is for the Ford DiagNow mobile app, which is
offered to users by
Ford Motor Company, One American Road, Dearborn, Michigan 48126 United
States of America (“
Policy
”).
This Policy
applies to the personal information we
collect through your use of the Ford DiagNow mobile app.
It covers Ford Motor Company
and its controlled affiliates
and subsidiaries (“
Ford
,” “
we
,” or “
us
”) that use the
personal information collected through your use of the Ford DiagNow
mobile
app.
United States Only.
This Privacy Policy applies to
the collection, use, and sharing of personal information only of individuals in
the United States.
This Policy does not apply to:
·
Other products, services, features, websites, mobile apps, platforms,
or properties that Ford owns or operates (including through its controlled
affiliates and subsidiaries) and that display, link to, or refer to their own
privacy policies, including the services provided through MotorCraftService.com;
·
The data practices of anyone other than Ford; or
·
Content, products, services, features, websites, mobile apps,
platforms, or properties that Ford doesn’t own or operate, as described in the
section “Other Services” below.
