Annual CCPA Metrics 2023
The following metrics cover January 1, 2023 through December 31, 2023:
Requests to Know / Access Requests:
- Received: 66
- Complied with in whole or in part (providing categories or specific pieces of personal information): 61
- Denied: 5
-Median number of days to substantive response: 30
Requests to Delete:
- Received: 96
- Complied with in whole or in part (deleting all personal information or personal information not subject to an exception): 89
- Denied: 7
- Median number of days to substantive response: 31
Requests to Opt-Out / Do Not Sell Requests:
- Received: 3,242
- Complied with in whole or in part: 3,242
- Median number of days to substantive response: 1
